        <mxCell id="snVdAdAGRgclmG33DyMa-1" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontStyle=1;fontSize=22;" value="&lt;font&gt;Project: Equipment Rental Management System&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="40" width="520" x="30" y="20" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="snVdAdAGRgclmG33DyMa-8" parent="1" style="shape=note;size=20;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;" value="&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Client:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;I want a system that can let &lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(30, 240, 255));&quot;&gt;customer&lt;/font&gt; send &lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(20, 255, 36));&quot;&gt;request to rent&lt;/font&gt; &lt;font style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 22, 38));&quot;&gt;equipment&lt;/font&gt; &lt;/font&gt;for a &lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(247, 255, 17));&quot;&gt;date range&lt;/font&gt;. The system should be able to let us &lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(31, 255, 15));&quot;&gt;upload new equipment&lt;/font&gt; to the system so &lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(35, 255, 28));&quot;&gt;customer can view our new equipment&lt;/font&gt;. Customer should also be able to&lt;font&gt; &lt;font style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: light-dark(#ffffff, var(--ge-dark-color, #121212));&quot;&gt;check&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(204, 204, 0)); color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(204, 204, 0));&quot;&gt;availability&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt; on the &lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 30, 68));&quot;&gt;equipments&lt;/font&gt;. If the &lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(51, 255, 51));&quot;&gt;equipments were ordered&lt;/font&gt; we hope to &lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(0, 255, 110));&quot;&gt;notify our staff&lt;/font&gt; to &lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(51, 255, 51));&quot;&gt;view the order&lt;/font&gt;, so the &lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(51, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;staff&lt;/font&gt; &lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(51, 255, 51));&quot;&gt;can decline the order or approve&lt;/font&gt; it. If approved the system &lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(40, 255, 33));&quot;&gt;automatic sends the notification to the client&lt;/font&gt;, with the&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;total amount of&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 51, 51));&quot;&gt;payment&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt; for deposit the equipments.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;background-color: transparent; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;After rented, customer will returned the equipments to the store. The system should be able to&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(51, 255, 51));&quot;&gt; auto calculate the rental fees&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; so that customer can pay the amount of money in store. Then our&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(51, 255, 255));&quot;&gt; techician&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; will come to &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 51, 51));&quot;&gt;inspect&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; damages. if there is one technician should be able to &lt;/span&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(33, 255, 62));&quot;&gt;report a &lt;span style=&quot;background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(255, 51, 51));&quot;&gt;damages&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; that ties to the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 0, 0));&quot;&gt;order&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;, and auto create both&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-family: Helvetica;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 51, 51));&quot;&gt;maintenance job&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(51, 255, 51));&quot;&gt;notice to our technician&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt; and &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(51, 255, 51));&quot;&gt;create payment to the damages of the equipment&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt; for our customer to pay.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(51, 255, 51));&quot;&gt; If all of it was done the order is consider completed&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Developer:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;What do expect for the client to view in your equipment page?&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Client:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;I was thinking giving them the &lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 51));&quot;&gt;equipment rental fee&lt;/font&gt;, &lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 102));&quot;&gt;equipment image&lt;/font&gt;, they are &lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 51));&quot;&gt;rented or in maintenance&lt;/font&gt; or not and about their &lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 153));&quot;&gt;conditions&lt;/font&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Developer:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Equipment might have many the same equipment model. How do the company usually distinguish them?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Client:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;We &lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(215, 255, 20));&quot;&gt;categories&lt;/font&gt; our equipment and each distinct equipment has their own &lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 102));&quot;&gt;assest tag&lt;/font&gt;, for example Camera 001 to distinguish them. It is the category plus the ID of the thing.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Developer:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;You mention deposit, damage and rental fee payment, what if they failed to pay the fee?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Client:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;The system should &lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(51, 255, 51));&quot;&gt;tag the payment as failed&lt;/font&gt; in that case, we dont accept the returned or customer to picked up that equipment. The system shouldn&#39;t be care about after the failed payment in rental fee or damages, we will handle it with our legal system.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Developer:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Is pretty common that customer will not return the equipment in time. What happened in that case?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Client:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;We would put a &lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 51));&quot;&gt;late per day fee&lt;/font&gt; for that equipment, and I think this fee should be &lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(51, 255, 51));&quot;&gt;able to view by the customer&lt;/font&gt;. If a late return happen system should &lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(51, 255, 51));&quot;&gt;c&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(51, 255, 51));&quot;&gt;alculate saperate fee that is about late return&lt;/font&gt; for customer to pay. I also acknowledge missing items that are rented out, in-order to &lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(0, 255, 0));&quot;&gt;track those items that exeeding 7 days late return, the system should list all of those order&lt;/font&gt; for our staff to contact the customer. After 10 days it will be handle by us not the system. And we possibily&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(51, 255, 51));&quot;&gt; will ban the customer in the system&lt;/font&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Developer:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;What happen if a customer come to the store and said the equipment was missing?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Client:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Then the technician should &lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(51, 255, 51));&quot;&gt;report it as damage, and the auto created&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(51, 255, 51));&quot;&gt;maintenance job should be flagged as unrepairable&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;. The damage payment should be &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 51));&quot;&gt;original price&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt; of the equipment, that I also think &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(0, 255, 0));&quot;&gt;customer should know prior renting&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Developer:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;You mention&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;maintenance job what happen after it was done?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Client:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(51, 255, 51));&quot;&gt;If all damages was repaired the equipment should be ready to rented out again&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;. Technician should be able to&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(51, 255, 51));&quot;&gt; report the final condition of the equipment after repaired to update the &lt;span style=&quot;background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(255, 255, 153));&quot;&gt;equipement status&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;. If &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(0, 255, 0));&quot;&gt;one of the damage is unrepairable we do not consider the equipment is able to rented out anymore&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Developer:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;You mention ban customer who has the ability to decide to do that?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Client:&lt;br&gt;That will be our &lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(0, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;admin&lt;/font&gt;. Who &lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(0, 255, 0));&quot;&gt;can do anything in the system aspect customer abilities&lt;/font&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="1130" width="1000" x="30" y="60" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
